<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Faculty Honored for Excellence at Founders' Day Ceremony</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">April 6, 2011</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2506/en_US/sweetmain40yr.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jason Greene</p>
			
			<p>Haven Sweet, associate dean of the College of Sciences, was recognized for his 40 years of service at UCF.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d449076490380a">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
								<h3>Story Images</h3>
								<ul id="story_images">
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d449076490380a&amp;img_mode=2&amp;index=0">
							<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2506/en_US/808news98.jpg"  />
						</a>
						</li>
						
						
					
			
					
						
						
							
						<li>
						<a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d449076490380a&amp;img_mode=2&amp;index=1">
